{"tid":589977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子遇車禍截肢 印度院方竟拿斷肢當枕頭","createTime":"2018-03-12T08:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T14:13:50.000Z","uid":3393,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"51a02b533870b39afd46b1354847ac9afe8dc020","tid":589977,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpMoTGa7.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpMoTGa7.jpg&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ668P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=e88384cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpMoTGa7.jpg&h=97212b44\" target=\"_blank\">http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpMoTGa7.jpg</a><br />\n印度某間醫院遭控訴拿傷者斷枝當枕頭使用。（圖擷自印度斯坦時報）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕印度北方邦一名男子上週六（10日），因為交通事故，導致左腿截肢，但院方竟將斷肢拿來讓傷者當「枕頭」躺，家屬多次要求院方更換卻遭拒絕，事後院長庫西客（Sadhna Kaushik）表示已成立調查小組，涉事的醫護人員目前均遭停職。<br />\n<br />\n據《印度斯坦時報》（Hindustan Times）報導，當地警方指出，現年28歲的甘希耶姆（Ghanshyam）是一名校車清潔工，當時校車為了閃避拖拉機，整輛側翻在馬路上，傷者隨即被送往醫院治療，最後院方將甘希耶姆受損嚴重的左腳截肢。<br />\n<br />\n家屬到達醫院探視時，驚見甘希耶姆的斷肢竟被院方拿來當「枕頭」使用，讓他躺在其上。但當時他正處於昏睡狀態，似乎不知道自己躺的枕頭就是自己斷掉的左腳。<br />\n<br />\n家屬指控，事後曾跟醫生反映更換真的枕頭數次，均遭到拒絕，最後家人受不了衝出去市場買枕頭，才讓斷枝被換下，事件曝光後引起當地社會譁然。<br />\n<br />\n院長事後聲稱，她在緊急病房中盤問30名職員，沒有人目擊此事。因此她認為這或許只是一場惡作劇。但經調查，共有4名醫生和護士涉案，現均已停職。<br />\n<br />\n相關影片請見：<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/03/11/2555506482209730745/640x360_MP4_2555506482209730745.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F2555506482209730745%2F640x360_MP4_2555506482209730745.mp4&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ668P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=98a8dbfa\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/03/11/2555506482209730745/640x360_MP4_2555506482209730745.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2362911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2362911&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ668P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=a5c84f98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2362911&h=40200917\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2362911</a>"},{"pid":"2610089139288c671fb19f5d7509fff7e61eb449","tid":589977,"uid":45772,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"我笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次要落地獄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb15f1190053d053d0ef208e202e9f315ba7d0b","tid":589977,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"印度style<br />\n<br />\n 夠環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a7f97901c1ab67b9c8fd8a50f0a2fae7879ec2","tid":589977,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"旁邊d 人仲要好淡定唔當一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db284fadd1a48eb08727f7f3e11ea303c73345f3","tid":589977,"uid":144546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"雖然單新聞好好笑好似笑片情節咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過如果我係家屬一定嬲到癲"},{"pid":"9e98ef57c6e742ae858db02de679f03243ad29af","tid":589977,"uid":138834,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T13:58:1